2019年10月9日下午，警方指四男一女保安涉在10月7日晚上阻止防暴警察進入新港城中心商場，被控「阻差辦公」而被捕，在馬鞍山警署扣查，同日晚上獲准保釋。警方又表示，根據《警隊條例》第63條，任何人士協助或意圖或拖延警務人員執法，循簡易程序定罪後，可處罰款$5,000及監禁6個月。<ref>{{cite news |title=新港城保安阻防暴警進商場　四男一女據報涉阻差辦公被捕 |url=https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E9%98%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/ |accessdate=2019-10-09 |publisher=立場新聞 |date=2019-10-09 |archive-date=2019-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112213320/https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E9%98%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>到晚上7時半，百多名市民到新港城中心商場二樓的天幕廣場內聲援，手持「支持盡忠職守保安員，強烈譴責警方濫權濫捕」標語。期間約40名防暴警察一度在新港城中心商場出現。<ref>{{cite news |title=馬鞍山警署近百防暴警衝出驅散市民 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191009/s00001/1570612157795/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e6%b8%af%e5%9f%8e%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%89%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e3%80%91%e9%a6%ac%e9%9e%8d%e5%b1%b1%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e8%bf%91%e7%99%be%e9%98%b2%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e8%a1%9d%e5%87%ba%e9%a9%85%e6%95%a3%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91 |accessdate=2019-10-09 |work=明報 |date=2019-10-09 |archive-date=2019-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009154639/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E/article/20191009/s00001/1570612157795/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%258E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%259D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

